Title: Determinant Line Bundles and Topological Invariants of Hyperbolic

Geometry - Expository RemarksAuthors: A.A. Bytsenko, M.C. Falleiros, A.E. Goncalves and Z.G. Kuznetsova

Comments: 10 pages. To appear in G@C, special issue devoted to QG, Unified

Models and Strings, to mark 100th Anniversary of Tomsk State PedagogicalUniversity. Editor - S.D. OdintsovJournal-ref: Grav.Cosmol. 8 (2002) 91-95

We give some remarks on twisted determinant line bundles and Chern-Simonstopological invariants associated with real hyperbolic manifolds. Index of atwisted Dirac operator is derived. We discuss briefly application of obtainedresults in topological quantum field theory.